headline.print_headline: Putin, Cameron Agree 'Peaceful Means' Only Way Out of Ukraine Crisis: Kremlin
headline.main: Putin, Cameron Agree 'Peaceful Means' Only Way Out of Ukraine Crisis: Kremlin

lead_paragraph: Russia's President Vladimir Putin and British Prime Minister David Cameron, in a phone call on Wednesday, agreed the Ukrainian crisis can only be solved through "peaceful means", the Kremlin said in a statement.
